		<div id="mw-content-text" class="mw-body-content mw-content-ltr" lang="en" dir="ltr"><div class="mw-parser-output"><p>If you're experiencing problems with connecting to your simulator software then please read this page carefully. If by checking all these options, the problem still exists, then please submit a <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://siminnovations.com/newsupport/support-ticket">support ticket</a> through our website.
</p>
